  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind Space</strong> is a first person shooter action game with RPG elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can walk, run, and slide through random generated levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >melee, shoot, and assasinate AI in stealth or in direct route combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade player, gadets, weapos, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect keycards, hack, and solve puzzles to open locked doors and find special Tokens!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several different AI types that scale with progress through the story.<br>Boss fights featuring bullet hell mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>Severl differect weapons including Rifle, Shotgun, Magnum, Bows, Orbital Bombardment Grendaes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon can be unlocked and upgraded using bits, including Damage, Fire rate, and Accuracy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rouglike Story elements adding levels of story different playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A find Tokens in a lore rich universe!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind Space</strong> is a first person shooter action game with RPG elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can walk, run, and slide through random generated levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >melee, shoot, and assasinate AI in stealth or in direct route combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade player, gadets, weapos, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect keycards, hack, and solve puzzles to open locked doors and find special Tokens!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several different AI types that scale with progress through the story.<br>Boss fights featuring bullet hell mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>Severl differect weapons including Rifle, Shotgun, Magnum, Bows, Orbital Bombardment Grendaes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon can be unlocked and upgraded using bits, including Damage, Fire rate, and Accuracy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rouglike Story elements adding levels of story different playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A find Tokens in a lore rich universe!</p>",
